bits

Class KSatReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • bits.KSatReader

  • public class KSatReader
extends java.lang.Object
    A reader which is created using an object of type positronic.satisfiability.elements.ISolver and has a method parseInstance which translates a positronic.satisfiability.elements.IProblem object into a corresponding org.sat4j.specs.IProblem object. For example, here's how a KSatReader might be used on a positronic.satisfiability.elements.IProblem called problem:

    ...

    ISolver solver = ... // some solver from a solver factory

    KSatReader reader = new KSatReader(solver);

    positronic.satisfiability.elements.IProblem problem = ... // some problem from KSat API

    org.sat4j.specs.IProblem sat4jproblem = reader.parseInstance(problem);

    if (sat4jproblem.isSatisfiable()) {

    ...

    }
